comment: Listener that gets notified when the progress changes.

methods.name: void onProgressUpdate(@NonNull TranscodingSession session, @IntRange(from = 0, to = 100) int progress)
methods.comment:
* Called when the progress changes. The progress is in percentage between 0 and 1,
             * where 0 means the session has not yet started and 100 means that it has finished.
             *
             * @param session      The session associated with the progress.
             * @param progress The new progress ranging from 0 ~ 100 inclusive.

methodNames: void onProgressUpdate(@NonNull TranscodingSession session, @IntRange(from = 0, to = 100) int progress)
